SYMBOL TIERS:
- TIER_1 (BTC/ETH/BNB): Highest liquidity, most predictable. Min confidence 0.70. Wider stop losses OK.
- TIER_2 (SOL/XRP/ADA etc.): Mid-cap alts. Min confidence 0.75. Standard risk.
- TIER_3 (DOGE/WIF/TAO etc.): Memecoins/low-cap. Min confidence 0.85. Require very strong confluence.
